  "comment": "$$2^x+\\frac{2^{x+2}}{2^x-4}+\\frac{4^x+7\\cdot 2^x+20}{4^x-3\\cdot 2^{x+2}+32}\\leq 1\\\\ 2^x+\\frac{4\\cdot 2^x}{2^x-4}+\\frac{4^x+7\\cdot 2^x+20}{4^x-12\\cdot 2^x+32}\\leq 1$$\nСделаем замену \\(t=2^x\\):\n$$t+\\frac{4t}{t-4}+\\frac{t^2+7t+20}{t^2-12t+32}\\leq 1\\\\ t+\\frac{4t}{t-4}+\\frac{t^2+7t+20}{(t-4)(t-8)}-\\frac{t^2-12t+32}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0\\\\ t+\\frac{4t(t-8)}{(t-4)(t-8)}+\\frac{19t-12}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0\\\\ \\frac{t(t-4)(t-8)}{(t-4)(t-8)}+\\frac{4t^2-13t-12}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0\\\\ \\frac{t(t-4)(t-8)}{(t-4)(t-8)}+\\frac{(t-4)(4t+3)}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0\\\\ \\frac{(t-4)(t^2-4t+3)}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0\\\\ \\frac{(t-4)(t-1)(t-3)}{(t-4)(t-8)}\\leq 0$$\nВоспользуемся методом интервалов:\nПолучаем три промежутка:\n$$t\\leq 1~или~3\\leq t<4~или~4<t<8\\\\ 2^x\\leq 1~или~3\\leq 2^x<4~или~4<2^x<8\\\\ x\\leq 0~или~\\log_23\\leq x<2~или~2<x<3$$\nОтвет: \\((-\\infty;0]\\cup [\\log_23;2)\\cup (2;3)\\)",
